data.description: Short sale! NEW ROOF in 2021- Large 4 bedroom home located in Porteaux Bay subdivision in St. Martin. This beautiful family home has so much to offer. Some of the features include a formal dining, large eat-in kitchen with beautiful windows, living room and great room, large front porch and back patio for grilling and chilling, wood burning fireplace, privacy fenced back yard with a separate detached mom-in-law suite with full bath, a double car garage  and so much more! A/C just serviced. Location is close to I10 and convenient to get to Downtown OS, Promenade, Ingalls, Keesler, not to mention entertainment and shopping.  Buyer to verify all info contained within.
